.4-inch LCD screen is backlit and easy to read."]},"id":"03f7a13f-129f-4917-a612-e160881db2a8","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Playback"},"id":"8cbf2105-db43-476c-9f4d-a7e24b6783a6","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/x2NGuN5DxEYvhD66hBN3FR.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"This voice recorder’s smooth design, rounded corners and beveled front make for a device that fits just right in your hand. It also fits easily into any shirt or pants pocket. The recorder has user-friendly features including a jack for an external microphone and another for earphones and a built-in 1-inch speaker.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/56981-philips-dvt4.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/x2NGuN5DxEYvhD66hBN3FR.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"x2NGuN5DxEYvhD66hBN3FR","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/x2NGuN5DxEYvhD66hBN3FR.jpg","alt":""},"id":"db15e177-e007-4a5c-be58-3aee1a2de8ba","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This digital voice recorder has three-mic recording technology. This system pulls sound from three locations at the same time. The center mic is omni-directional and captures front, left and right, while the two side microphones pull sound from right and left, front and back. A podcaster or independent filmmaker will love this feature because it will make the sound feel 3D, as if you are standing in the middle of a conversation, surrounded by sound.","This digital recorder has variable-speed playback to make reviewing audio recordings simple. Its track-marking feature lets you highlight portions of a recording to make them easy to find and return to later. The device has voice-activated recording that puts it to sleep and reactivates it when someone speaks, saving battery life and storage space.","The Philips DVT5500 records MP3, MPEG and WAV files, which are all great audio formats for different reasons. MP3s and MPEGs are more compressed than WAV files and are easier to transfer over the internet. WAV files, on the other hand, take longer to upload but typically have higher sound quality, though the average listener will have a hard time distinguishing between these audio formats.<br/><br/>"]},"id":"3814dbf0-9331-4294-b339-20d28f12a71c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Storage &amp; Battery Life"},"id":"32fb8128-0b58-4594-972f-acbb0408a077","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/FSbNQeyk4SUeqE4rFctgMB.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The Philips DVT5500’s 4GB built-in storage capacity and maximum recording time is one of the best internal storage features on the market. Its maximum recording time of 1,140 hours is about double its nearest rival. The SD expandable storage slot adds even more potential, and an 8GB card is included. You’ll never run out of space on this device. The ability to transfer files onto any PC or Mac via the USB and SD card and then delete it from the original source only increases the storage capacity potential.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/56981-philips-dvt5.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/FSbNQeyk4SUeqE4rFctgMB.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"FSbNQeyk4SUeqE4rFctgMB","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/FSbNQeyk4SUeqE4rFctgMB.jpg","alt":""},"id":"bbd31cdf-6953-4685-8a4d-9bfae794662c","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Philips DVT1000 recorder has many of the same features and is also a great and even more affordable recorder. The DVT1000 has a more standard two-mic recording feature and less internal storage, and its only recording format is MP3. It does have the SD card slot, but no card is included in the package. It also has far fewer accessories. The DVT5500 has a USB cable, nice earbud headphones with a pause button on the cord, a remote control, rechargeable batteries, a pouch and a quick start guide. The DVT1000 accessories are limited to rechargeable batteries, USB cable and quick start guide."]},"id":"19331955-9018-42ec-97d7-e2bd5354e4fc","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"b4a39b26-bda9-4d36-8a7e-b5fc0a58df90","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/f7eMQKMk8jMwqUBVfa7SsK.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Philips has excellent customer support. Questions and concerns are addressed quickly through Philips&#39; 24-hour online chat service through the company&#39;s website. All you need is internet access and a computer. Chat representatives respond in real time. If they don&#39;t know the answers, they&#39;ll find them or refer you to a company rep who does. The quick start guide the recorder comes with could be a little less minimalistic. It’s all in pictures and a little explanation would be nice. But fortunately the online manual makes up for it and is very informative and helpful.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/56981-philips-dvt9.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/f7eMQKMk8jMwqUBVfa7SsK.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"f7eMQKMk8jMwqUBVfa7SsK","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/f7eMQKMk8jMwqUBVfa7SsK.jpg","alt":""},"id":"d5343ddf-7c95-464d-87ef-e93d6b42612c","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["A comprehensive FAQs section is available on the Philips website, and extremely helpful customer representatives answer email queries within a day. You also may call the phone number listed under Support on the website. Phone hours are from 9 a.m. to 9 p.m. Eastern time, Monday through Saturday, and from 9 a.m. to 6 p.m. on Sunday. Major holidays are excluded."]},"id":"b2ddb6df-1673-4561-87b9-2d1726ddd51c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"2906d1d4-7678-4893-9a1f-c89a4b09ac3d","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["It’s easy to see why the Philips DVT5500 is our top digital voice recorder. It&#39;s the lightest and among the most compact of the products we reviewed. Its internal and expanded storage capacity combine for 12GB and thousands of hours. It’s 